## SSPL Key Provision (Section 13)

If you make the functionality of the Program available to third parties as
a service, you must make all Source Code for the program available to them
under this license, including all modifications and any infrastructure code
you use to make the functionality available.

This provision ensures that companies benefiting from this software contribute
back to the community or obtain a commercial license.
